caption: A white round plate is on a table with a plastic tablecloth on it.  Two foil covered food halves are on the white plate along with a serving of golden yellow french fries.  Next to the white plate in a short,  topless, plastic container is a white sauce.  Diagonal to the white plate are the edges of several other stacked plates.  There are black shadows reflected on the table.

There are four small pizzas on a brown wooden plate.  There are greens in the center for garnish.  The small pizzas have broccoli, red peppers and cheese for toppings.  The wooden plate is sitting on a white table top.

A black and white cat is sitting in a white chair. The cat is looking up at the camera. There is a black cord and a black strap on the floor in front of the chair. There is another piece of white furniture next to the chair.

A boy is practicing his skateboard moves outside of a driveway.  The cars parked behind him indicate that he is in front of a motel or an apartment house.  The boy is dressed in blue jeans and a gray sweatshirt with a silkscreen print on the front, thought it can't be made out what it is.  He is wearing black skater shoes and a baseball cap.  His face can't be seen because it is blocked by the hat's bill.  He is very intent on learning this turn on flat ground.
Two brown horses are standing together outside. There heads are up against the side of the building. The both have saddles on. They are standing on concrete.

A couple is sitting on a bench along a path in a park setting. They face a small green lake. Over the lake is a red bridge on stilts with multicolored flags on staffs at intervals on the bridge walkway. The park is filled with trees and shrubs and the sky is overcast.

A silver train is on the ground. There is graffiti on the bottom of the train. There are rocks and grass next to the train.
